title: Fresh Chicken Breasts
body: Enjoy our fresh & tender chicken breasts, made with hormone-free & grain-fed chickens, sourced from the most sustainable Egyptian suppliers. Have them grilled, pan-fried or baked in the oven. Serve with Gourmet Roasted Vegetables, Gourmet Mashed Potato or your favorite Gourmet fresh salad for a delicious & filling meal!

title: Fresh Chicken Escalope
body: Fresh and juicy premium chicken escalope that can be enjoyed fried, breaded or rolled. Delicious in every bite. For a hearty, yummy meal, add a tasty mushroom sauce and some mashed potatoes as a side. It's that simple!

title: Fresh Chicken Leg
body: Makes the perfect quick dinner fix and great party food! Can be cooked in so many different ways. Delicious caramelised and baked in the oven (use your preferred marinade for a juicy glaze) or breaded and fried. Serve with Gourmet Dip It Tzatziki and your preferred Gourmet fresh salad. Our chicken are sourced from the most sustainable Egyptian suppliers, they are hormone free and grain fed.

title: Fresh Whole Chicken
body: Enjoy our fresh whole chicken, hormone free & grain fed sourced from the most sustainable Egyptian suppliers. We recommend serving our whole chicken roasted in the oven with fresh rosemary, carrots & baby potatoes. Serve with Gourmet Mashed Potato with Nutmeg and Gourmet Roasted Vegetables for a delicious and easy-to-prepare meal!

title: Fresh Chicken Wings
body: Enjoy our fresh chicken wings, made with hormone free & grain fed chickens, sourced from the most sustainable Egyptian suppliers. We recommend serving our chicken wings baked in the oven with a splash of BBQ and Worcestershire sauce!

title: Fresh Chicken Liver
body: Our fresh chicken liver, made with hormone free & grain fed chickens and sourced from the most sustainable Egyptian suppliers.

title: Frozen Whole Egyptian Chicken
body: Tender and juicy, this premium Egyptian whole chicken, is sourced only from the most sustainable suppliers and naturally grain fed. Serve roasted with baby potatoes, garlic and fresh rosemary.

title: Chilled Turkey Breast Slices
body: Our premium quality turkey breast fillets are ready to cook. Season with your favourite herbs & condiments and pop them in the oven for a delicious meal or fry them for scrumptious turkey pane!

title: Roast Turkey Breast
body: Our premium quality roast turkey breasts are ready to cook. Season with your favorite herbs and condiments and pop them in the oven for a scrumptious meal!

title: Fresh Boneless Turkey Breast
body: Boneless turkey breasts are a delicious alternative to your regular protein. It also makes a great substitute when you don't have time to took an entire turkey. The breast's tender white meat makes it a great base for your preferred seasoning mix and they are easy to cook. For a scrumptious taste, serve with our turkey stuffing and ready to heat mashed potatoes and gravy. Cooking Tip: Marinating the turkey breast for at least an hour before cooking makes it juicy and flavorful.

title: Fresh Chicken Drumstick
body: Enjoy our fresh chicken drumsticks, made with hormone free & grain fed chickens, sourced from the most sustainable Egyptian suppliers. We recommend serving our juicy drumsticks baked in the oven with fresh parsley & roasted garlic.

title: Fresh Chicken Breast with Lemon & Garlic
body: The skinless chicken breasts are perfectly seasoned and ready-to-cook for a quick and easy meal. We marinated our fresh chicken breasts with lemon and garlic for an appetising and juicy taste. Excellent option for mid-week lunch or dinner, simply heat your skillet and voila! Serve with our ready-to-heat mashed potatoes or roasted vegetables for a full-fledged delicious meal!

title: Butterflied Tandoori Chicken
body: Craving a flavoursome Indian meal? Look no further! This tender and juicy chicken is beautifully seasoned with Indian spices giving it a rich and full aroma. Add a side basmati rice for a truly authentic Tandoori meal.

title: Fresh Chicken Shawerma
body: For a quick & simple gourmet meal, marinate this Fresh Chicken Shawerma with your favourite seasonings and grill to your delight. Serve with a side of Gourmet Oriental Hummus for a delicious meal.

title: Chicken Shish Tawook - 1kg
body: Serve your guest a grand feast with the Chicken Shish Tawook. It looks tempting and tastes delicious. It is a perfect pick for those who do not have time for cooking from the start

title: Chicken Thighs with Bone - 1kg
body: The Chicken Thighs with Bone can be used to prepare various delicious and nutritious meals. You can use them as a whole to deep fry, shallow fry, or roast in casseroles or stews. You can also strip off the bone and can utilize the meat in stir-fries.

title: Frozen Chicken Thighs
body: Juicy and full of flavour, our chicken thighs are a favorite for those who prefer dark chicken meat. They are delicious baked in the oven with fresh herbs. These chicken thighs are 100% natural and organic from grain fed, hormone-free chicken from sustainable local farms.

title: Oriental Chicken Leg
body: Enjoy our frozen chicken drumsticks, made with hormone free & grain fed chickens, sourced from the most sustainable Egyptian suppliers. We recommend serving our juicy drumsticks baked in the oven with fresh parsley & roasted garlic.

title: Frozen Premium Butterflied Quai
body: Enjoy our two very premium Halal quails! We recommend cooking them on the grill or baked in the oven with a side of Gourmet roasted veggies or mashed potatoes for an easy to prepare meal.

title: Greek Chicken Souvlaki
body: Gourmetâ€™s Chicken Souvlaki is about to take your taste buds on a delightful Greek escapade. Cook the chicken, add some Tzatziki sauce and a side of salad and fries, and enjoy this Greek staple from the comfort of your home.
